I"a<p>You have two network cables plug in the back of a server and you want to know which one is eth0? Use the following command and the interface light will start blinking (for 10 seconds) on the chosen adapter.</p>

<blockquote>
  <p># ethtool -p eth0 10</p>
</blockquote>

<p>This command can be run without disturbing the traffic on the interface.</p>
